 <style>
    .header {
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #eeeeee;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .balance-info {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #e6f7ff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border: 1px solid #b3e0ff;
    }

    .balance-info p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .balance-info span {
        font-size: 36px;
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>
<div class="header">
    <h1>Your Token Balance Update</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= user %>,</p>
    <p>This is a quick update to let you know about your current token balance. Tokens are used for all our services, so you'll want to make sure you have enough to keep going.</p>
</div>

<div class="balance-info">
    <p>Your current token balance is:</p>
    <span><%= tokens %></span>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <p>If you're running low, don't worry! You can easily purchase more tokens from your account dashboard to continue
        enjoying our services without interruption.</p>
</div>

<div class="button-container">
    <a href="https://partner.lui2mi.com//dashboard/tokens" class="button">Buy More Tokens</a>
</div>